{"tid":1746590,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"正式宣布 禮拜日鳩叫回歸","createTime":"2019-11-22T21:00:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T05:53:51.000Z","uid":138940,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0834ff306dc6ae2b9a24e118982744a79721f56e","tid":1746590,"uid":138940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T21:00:27.000Z","msg":"話說禮拜日朝早7:30就要投票，唔知建制會用d咩手段阻止選舉進行，一定要盡早去投。<br />\n<br />\n作為年輕人一份子，都知道大家習慣夜訓，然後第二日訓到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>所以！我宣布鳩叫正式回歸！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n不過係朝早7點開始鳩叫<span style=\"color: green;\">「起身落街食早餐喇」</span> 之類去叫醒人<br />\n<br />\nps. 手足最好係個冇乜人見到既位先叫，或者叫完就run<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"311473d659b3e766f7eb35db8c256dc494449331","tid":1746590,"uid":138940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T21:00:58.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"32f722b4cb58d6e87a451e96155d1fab29de9bcc","tid":1746590,"uid":138940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T21:01:09.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"91aa5e2d2ad5318fb30daccc608623bbf66d431b","tid":1746590,"uid":138940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T21:01:21.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"d05eeb4323b70538f3f176b3c7aab06c4ffa1f93","tid":1746590,"uid":138940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T21:01:31.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"b22f44e31ea8f2a5a3fe4f2cb971cae69c808146","tid":1746590,"uid":138940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T21:01:47.000Z","msg":"大家係咪訓曬喇"},{"pid":"4077a6c5d5e1d4c39032a34991a1560a252e8d7d","tid":1746590,"uid":138940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T21:01:57.000Z","msg":"屌原來已經五點"},{"pid":"018ec5d14e014eda0941c6b998a85d0b22f34c86","tid":1746590,"uid":138940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy